ch.uzh.agglorecommender.clusterer

Class TreeBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.uzh.agglorecommender.clusterer.TreeBuilder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Observable, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Runnable

    public final class TreeBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, Observable, java.lang.Runnable
    Implementation of COBWEB inspired hierarchical agglomerative two-dimensional clustering algorithm for media recommendation generation. The model component of the M-V-C-pattern used for the clustering subsystem. (M:TreeBuilder-V:TreeVisualizer-C:ClusteringController)
    See Also:

                                        IMaxCategoryUtilitySearcher mcus)

      • merge

        private INode merge(IMergeResult mergeResult,
          IClusterSet<INode> openSet)
        Creates a new node and initializes the nodes attributes based on a list of close nodes. The list of close nodes become the children of the new node.
        Parameters:
        mergeResult - close nodes which are used to initialize a new node and will form the new nodes children. These nodes are removed from the open set.
        openSet - the set of nodes to which the new node is added and from which the merged nodes are removed.
        Returns:
        a new node which has the nodesToMerge as children.
